D. Acquisition Strategy
The Prophet Research and Development (R&D) Acquisition Strategy is structured to maintain operational relevancy of Prophet Enhanced systems in a dynamic threat
environment while reducing risk and streamlining business and engineering processes. Contracting activities are to maintain SIGINT relevance and complete TIs to
Prophet Enhanced systems to pursue the latest SOIs and design against obsolescence annually. The TI contract supports R&D and other developmental work.




