       In FY 2024, decrease of $14.400 million was due to a Congressional directed transfer to RDT&E, Space Force, PE 0601103SF, University Research Initiatives,
       for space unique S&T.

       In FY 2024, decrease of $6.719 million in Other Adjustments was due to realignment of funds to PE 0602212F, Defense Laboratories R&D Projects, to implement
       the Department of Defense (DoD) Funding Laboratory Enhancements Across Four Categories (FLEX-4) authority under 10 U.S.C Section 4123.

