power projection and rapid deployment mission. WGS provides high-capacity tactical end-to-end connectivity and interoperability with strategic networks and national
decision-makers, satisfying JCS network operations in support of the President, JCS, combatant commanders, military departments, Department of State and other
government departments and agencies. This requirement supports the Army 2030 / 2040 Strategic Plan.

