MILSATCOM capacity demands in support of JADC2, Digital IF to enable resiliency and path diversity and Interference
Cancellation to improve reliability of SATCOM communication links. Additionally, complete development of testing units in order to
begin First Article Test and Wideband Global SATCOM (WGS) system certification.

