and software builds. Hypersonic technology maturation, risk reduction and system engineering activities will be completed to support preliminary design development
and testing of the missile concept. Develop missile with Japan as part of a cooperative development effort. Aegis Weapon System upgrades to leverage the Glide
Phase Interceptor for regional hypersonic glide phase defense will continue to mature including work toward system level preliminary design incorporating one missile
