requirements.
- Perform HD lethality range testing and material characterization.
- Provide limited test analysis and M&S framework development.

Specific and/or unique accomplishments to each FY are as follows:

FY 2025 Plans:
Aegis Weapon System
- Evolve and mature systems engineering efforts to flow system level requirements to subsystem requirement specifications and
begin preliminary design activities.
- Develop updated weapon system code to support demonstration of capability in partner flight tests and flight experiments.
- Continue refinement of engagement and shot selection algorithms to optimize performance across the Glide Phase Interceptor
threat and battlespace.

