the DoD’s migration towards more agile development and acquisition of IT capabilities. This provides T&E support, including
infrastructure, testing capabilities and events, policies, and processes to Regional Combatant Commands (COCOMs), Military
Services, DoD Agencies, other Federal Government agencies, private industry, Coalition partners and allies.

