FY 2025 Plans:
Will continue to provide cybersecurity testing to maintain accreditation and Authority-To-Operate (ATO) approvals to remain
operational. Additionally, will provide integration testing of technology refreshed End-of-Life/End-of-Support hardware and
software as well as testing version updates on hardware and software items. JRSS stacks need testing to remain operational until
they are sunset by FY 2027.
