N/A
FY 2025 to FY 2026 Increase/Decrease Statement:
Decrease commensurate with Portfolio Management, Modernization and Capabilities (PM2C) Council and DoD Services directed
JRSS decommissioning efforts. JRSS will only conduct bare minimum Tech Refresh of critical components, allowing for continued
operational capability of JRSS functionality for remaining on board JRSS users. JRSS had minimal testing requirements requiring
RDT&E funding due to the continued progression of JRSS sunset activities.
